    <section class="intro" id="learn-more">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What is Computer Engineering?</h2>
        <p>
          Computer Engineering is a field that integrates electrical engineering
          and computer science to develop computer hardware and software.
          Computer engineers are involved in many hardware and software aspects
          of computing, from the design of individual microprocessors, personal
          computers, and supercomputers, to circuit design.
        </p>
